OL,3,CInvestigation underway after man in
OL,4,Chis 80s dies in house fire
OL,6,FCumbria Police has launched an
OL,7,Finvestigation following a fatal house
OL,8,Ffire.
OL,10,FA man in his 80s died at the scene of
OL,11,Fthe incident in the Salterbeck area of
OL,12,FWorkington on Thursday 25 June.
OL,14,FPolice had been contacted at around
OL,15,F6:31 that evening with a report of a
OL,16,Ffire on Poole Road.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/3
