OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F325A1782733687
OL,3,CInvestigation underway after man in
OL,4,Chis 80s dies in house fire
OL,6,FThree fire engines attended the
OL,7,Fincident, from Workington, Whitehaven
OL,8,Fand Maryport fire stations, as well as
OL,9,Fa joint incident command unit from
OL,10,FPenrith.
OL,12,FFirefighters used two breathing
OL,13,Fapparatus, two hose reel jets, and a
OL,14,Fpositive pressure ventilation fan to
OL,15,Fextinguish the fire.
OL,17,FThe service was in attendance for
OL,18,Fabout six hours, and a police cordon
OL,19,Fwas erected around the scene.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/3
