OL,3,CInvestigation underway after man in
OL,4,Chis 80s dies in house fire
OL,6,FCumbria Constabulary and Cumbria Fire
OL,7,Fand Rescue Service are now conducting
OL,8,Fa joint investigation to establish the
OL,9,Fcauses and circumstances of the fire.
OL,11,FOfficers are asking anyone who may
OL,12,Fhave witnessed the incident, or who
OL,13,Fhas relevant information or footage to
OL,14,Fcontact the police service.
